; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures SCU PWR and enters deep-sleep sub mode 2.
;    And it do reset a target device from PA0 by external rising edge signal.
;
; B. Preparation
;    Connecting target port with a suitable instrument.
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    1. SCUPWR
;
; For more information, read a user's manual of the target device carefully.
;
; SCUPWR
; 1. PWR                        : [ d h 0 h 0 2 0x1]
;    Power Mode                 : d (Deep Sleep 1)
;    Sleep Clock Source         : h (HSI)
;    Sleep Clock Source Divide  : 0
;    Wakeup Clock Source        : h (HSI)
;    Wakeup Clock Source Divide : 0
;    Deep Sleep Sub Mode        : 2 (sub mode 2)
;    Wake-up Pin                : 0x1 (PA0)
;
; SCUPWR
sendln 'cm scupwr'
mpause 30
sendln 'pwr d h 0 h 0 2 0x1'
